{"tid":751992,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"補丫丫 有感","createTime":"2018-07-22T11:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T14:56:28.000Z","uid":170668,"like":114,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"336298b02a0c9502c4358bd4b7e6e895cbf14a94","tid":751992,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"2016，年，中文成績頗為，強差，人意，的，一年。<br />\n<br />\n在燈塔的廣告攻勢下，讓我遇見了你&mdash;林 X 欣。<br />\n<br />\n堂上的談笑風生，配上一番<span style=\"color: red;\">人生感言</span>，也有<span style=\"color: green;\">珍珠奶茶</span>的點綴，讓我漸漸<span style=\"color: violet;\">愛</span>上了你。<br />\n<br />\n今年，是我上陣的年份，有沒有未盡力，於心有愧？<br />\n沒有<br />\n<br />\nReg齊course？由2016reg到2018intensive <br />\n<br />\n出席演繹中文？有出席<br />\n<br />\n親手整禮物？有整<br />\n<br />\n去camp？有去<br />\n<br />\n合照？有影<br />\n<br />\n做到這個份上，自問已經問心無愧了，雖然中文成績不似預期，只有2級，但在我的眼中已經5**了。 我會一直追隨你的腳步，入讀asso中文系，將來加入Team。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這，就是我的老師&mdash;林 X 欣。<br />\n<br />\n22-7-2018."},{"pid":"3f24bceadce1e360ed3430e90b7ae112cd168728","tid":751992,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438dcd92539f296082b3494e007a19a0799d1017","tid":751992,"uid":151512,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf7cb6cbda1a0ad622077d57b90948130fbc55e","tid":751992,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"438dcd92539f296082b3494e007a19a0799d1017","tid":751992,"uid":151512,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"補YY得罪你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806582ebb1376d7dca8546a6dbf809a8e407f805","tid":751992,"uid":179571,"like":2,"dislike":0,